<% include ./partials/header %>

  <div class="card card-body text-center">
    <div class="card card-body text-center">

      <div class="aboutcard d-flex flex-row text-start">
        <div class="otherhalf card card-body fs-4">
          <p>
          <h1>QualityHotel</h1>is the leading and fastest growing family hotel chain in the Budget & Economy sector in United Kingdom. Established in Gloucester, UK, 2022, the group has today 4 hotels across the country.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hotelimg"><img src="/imgs/other/1 (2).jpg" alt=""></div>
      </div>


      <div class="aboutcard d-flex flex-row text-start mt-5">
        <div class="otherhalf card card-body fs-4">
          <p class="motto"><span class="bigletter">W</span>e offers warm, modern and affordable accommodation. This "Only For Everyone" concept proposes to both business and leisure clients a combination of comfort, design and high quality services at an attractive price: comfortable beds, high-speed WiFi, gourmet buffet breakfast.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="aboutcard d-flex flex-row text-start mt-4">
        <div class="otherhalf card card-body fs-4 mt-4">
          <p>Contemporary style hotels, interior design customized to local destinations, quality bedding, unlimited buffet breakfast with a wide choice of quality and organic products, high-speed Wi-Fi access, private parkings and 24-hour access to the rooms are just some of the features that our customers appreciate in our hotels. Chromecast in bedrooms can also be found in a selected number of hotels.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hotelimg"><img src="/imgs/other/1 (3).jpg" alt=""></div>
      </div>

      <div class="aboutcard d-flex flex-row text-start mt-4">
        <div class="hotelimg"><img src="/imgs/other/1 (4).jpg" alt="" style="transform: rotate(-35deg);"></div>
        <div class="otherhalf card card-body fs-4 mt-4">
          <p>Our Wedding specialists are looking forward to your wedding celebration. They offer a range of packages designed to suit a variety of needs and budgets. Wedding package features and options include the use of the on-site ceremony locations, evening reception facilities, in-house catering, and overnight accommodation for you and your guests.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="aboutcard d-flex flex-row text-start mt-4">
        <div class="otherhalf card card-body fs-4 mt-4">
          <p>Although each hotel brings its own unique personality to the collection, the overall ethos is the same, a passion for providing and sharing a great service, history, natural environment and locally sourced food.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hotelimg"><img src="/imgs/other/1 (5).jpg" alt=""></div>
      </div>

